Launch Readiness Criteria
## GO/NO-GO CHECKLIST

### Critical (Must Pass)
- [ ] All authentication tests pass
- [ ] Bet creation and acceptance work correctly
- [ ] Payment and withdrawal flows functional
- [ ] No security vulnerabilities found
- [ ] Data integrity maintained in all scenarios
- [ ] System handles expected load

### High Priority
- [ ] Admin functionalities operational
- [ ] Real-time notifications working
- [ ] Mobile responsiveness verified
- [ ] Error handling graceful
- [ ] All templates render correctly

### Medium Priority
- [ ] Performance meets requirements
- [ ] Usability feedback addressed
- [ ] Documentation complete
- [ ] Monitoring configured
- [ ] Backup procedures tested

## LAUNCH DECISION:
□ GO - All critical and high priority criteria met
□ NO-GO - Critical issues remain unresolved




